Package org.nasdanika.common.resources

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BinaryContainer
    Binding of container to InputStream.
    BinaryEntity
    Binding of entity state to InputStream.
    BinaryEntityContainer
    Binds EntityContainer to InputStream and BinaryEntity.
    BinaryResource
    Resource bound to BinaryEntity to serve as a common super-interface for BinaryEntity and BinaryEntityContainer.
    Container<E>
    Container of entries and other containers provides an abstraction for dealing with hierarchies/trees.
    Container.Copier<T,R>  
    Entity<T,E>
    Entity is something which has externalizable state.
    EntityContainer<C,E extends Entity<C,E>>
    Container of Entityies.
    Merger
    Merges new and old content of a BinaryEntity.
    Repository  
    Resource<E>
    Resource typically represents something with a lifespan longer than the JVM.
    ResourceContainer<E extends Resource<?>>
    Container of resources.
    TypedEntity<T>
    Binding of entity state to T, and of E to TypedeEntity<T>.
    TypedEntityContainer<T>
    Binds EntityContainer to T and TypedEntity<T>.
    TypedResource<T>
    Resource bound to TypedEntity to serve as a common super-interface for TypedEntity and TypedEntityContainer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryContainerImpl
    Delegates all calls to the target.
    ContainerFilter<E>  
    EphemeralBinaryEntity  
    EphemeralBinaryEntityContainer
    MapContainer of EphemeralEntityies.
    EphemeralEntity<T>
    Entity with the state stored in memory.
    EphemeralEntityContainer<T>
    MapContainer of EphemeralEntityies.
    FileSystemContainer
    Wrapper for a file system directory.
    FileSystemEntity
    Wrapper for a file system file.
    FileSystemResource
    Wrapper for File.
    MapContainer<E>
    Container backed by a map.
